institution: Human Resources Development Service of Korea
category: Ministry of Employment and Labor Consignment Project Subsidy Processing Rules/Article 9 (applicable mutatis mutandis)
contents: Article 9 (Application mutatis mutandis) The National Treasury Management Act, the Enforcement Decree of the same Act, the Enforcement Rules of the same Act, the Accounting Regulations and the Enforcement Rules of the Accounting Regulations apply to matters not specified in these rules.
